history.content: I took 162 and 161 together with the same instructors so I can comment on my experience for that. The projects do take time and especially when midterms and deadlines start to overlap it will become tough. But, the most important thing is to have a good 162 group and you all communicate with each other and have the same priorities. My entire group was taking both 161 and 162 so we basically had the same schedule and were able to plan things out in advance. I think both classes are definitely doable and complement each other nicely. Also, I would not worry about 195 at all.

Hello,

How do you find the following schedule?

Any thoughts/comments? (Should I leave it as it is, or adjust a little bit: like maybe add a course or replace astro C10 with an easier breadth)
